      $( [23-Nov-2003] $)

    $( The power class of the union of two classes is a subset of the union of
       their power classes, iff one class is a subclass of the other.  Exercise
       4.12(l) of [Mendelson] p. 235. $)
    pwssun $p |- ( ( A C_ B \/ B C_ A ) <->
